data.description: Now you can own in the prestigious Magnolia Place development in Sun N Lakes. This is one of the most stylish homes on the block with it's brand new $85,000 Concrete Barrel Tile Roof in 2023, virtually indestructible. Modern open split floor plan with 12' vaulted ceiling and 8' doors. Custom features like Trey ceilings, angled ceramic tile floors, formal dining room, crown molding with lights, 5' baseboards, rounded walls, upgraded ceiling fans with remote controls and more. The kitchen features real wood cabinets with sliders, under counter lights, granite countertops, garbage disposal, recessed lighting and the appliances are all less than 4 years old. Dining room has a dry bar (coffee bar).  The master bedroom is huge and has 2 walk-in closets, Trey ceiling, the master bath has a walk-in Shower, double sink, water closet and linen closet. Two large guest bedrooms both with new carpet one with a computer desk which is included. The guest bath has a shower tub with glass doors. If you enjoy a screened porch, go out the hurricane proof glass doors onto the back screened porch with paver floors for the luxury patio upgrade. City water and city sewer, well irrigation. The electric averages $140 a month. The lawn is fertilized and pest controlled on regular basis. There is a community pool in Sun N Lakes for residents. Clubhouse and restaurant. Best golf courses with Deer Run and Turtle Run. Close to all shopping and restaurants. Your own police and fire department. Close to Advent Hospital which is the largest hospital in the county. The home has been appraised so bring your best offer. No smokers or pets have lived in this house.
